libyuv
------------------------------------------
This is an open source project that includes YUV conversion and scaling
functionality. Converts all webcam formats to YUV (I420). Convert YUV to
formats for rendering/effects. Rotate by 90 degrees to adjust for mobile
devices in portrait mode. Scale YUV to prepare content for compression, with
point, bilinear or box filter.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  libjpeg8-1.5.3-1
  libstdc++6-7.4.0-1
  libyuv-devel-0+git20190506-1bl1
  libyuv0-0+git20190506-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.6.2-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://chromium.googlesource.com/libyuv/libyuv/

Canonical download:
  https://chromium.googlesource.com/libyuv/libyuv

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libyuv-0+git20190506-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libyuv-0+git20190506-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libyuv-0+git20190506-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libyuv-0+git20190506-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libyuv0-0+git20190506-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libyuv-devel-0+git20190506-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

